vides an abstraction layer for data transmission, allowing for flexibility and extensibility. The architecture emphasizes modularity and separation of concerns, making the system maintainable and scalable. The use of MQTT makes the system easy to integrate with other IoT platforms. The presence of tests indicates a focus on code quality and reliability.\n"}
